PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of YVON LeBLANC of Bouctouche, New Brunswick, as a director of the Board of Directors of VIA Rail Canada Inc. to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Douglas Shippee, whose term has expired.
